com.hazelcast.spi.impl.merge

Class SplitBrainDataSerializerHook

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.spi.impl.merge.SplitBrainDataSerializerHook
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSerializerHook

    public final class SplitBrainDataSerializerHook
extends Object
implements DataSerializerHook
    Contains all the ID hooks for IdentifiedDataSerializable classes used by the split-brain framework.

    SplitBrainMergePolicy classes are mapped here. This factory class is used by the internal serialization system to create IdentifiedDataSerializable classes without using reflection.

    Since:
    3.10
